title: Lupe 2003 (The Seaman's Wife)
description:
Lupe ( Andrea del Rosario) and Manolo (Leandro Munoz) are a young couple whose marriage life is about to undergo a drastic change when Manolo leaves for another country.

Left all alone through uneventful days and empty nights, Lupe tries to suppress her sexual needs.

A task that is, as Lupe will soon discover, easier said than done especially when Elmo (Jordan Herrera), an attractive young man, enters her life and awakens her primal urges.
